OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772052053
OL,3,CYouTuber's 'live' stream shown to
OL,4,Cmurder trial jury
OL,6,FThe jury in the trial of a man accused
OL,7,Fof the murder of Natalie McNally were
OL,8,Fplayed part of a video involving the
OL,9,Faccused playing video games
OL,10,Fpurportedly live on the night the
OL,11,FLurgan woman was allegedly murdered.
OL,13,FProsecutors believe the video was
OL,14,Fcreated by Stephen McCullagh as a
OL,15,F"false alibi".
OL,17,FMcCullagh, 36, of Woodland Gardens in
OL,18,FLisburn, denies murdering his former
OL,19,Fpartner Miss McNally, who was 15 weeks
OL,20,Fpregnant with their child.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
