OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772052053
OL,3,CYouTuber's 'live' stream shown to
OL,4,Cmurder trial jury
OL,6,FIn the stream, Mr McCullagh refers to
OL,7,Fbeing 'live' numerous times on Sunday
OL,8,F18th December 2022.
OL,10,FThroughout it, he explains how the
OL,11,Flive chat to allow people to join in
OL,12,Fthe stream was not working and he
OL,13,Fcan't check his phone for live chat
OL,14,Fcomments because of his internet.
OL,16,FMcCullagh also states he is having a
OL,17,Ffew drinks because "come on it's
OL,18,FSunday night" and how he shouldn't
OL,19,Fwhistle because it's very bad during
OL,20,Flive streaming.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772052053
OL,3,CYouTuber's 'live' stream shown to
OL,4,Cmurder trial jury
OL,6,FWhen arrested in February 2023, he
OL,7,Fwould later admit to police that the
OL,8,Ffootage of himself playing video games
OL,9,Fwas in fact recorded days before and
OL,10,Fnot live.
OL,12,FThe prosecution believe he "peddled
OL,13,Fthis false alibi" and Mr McCullagh
OL,14,Fmade his way to Natalie's home and
OL,15,Fmurdered her.
OL,17,FMiss McNally was found strangled,
OL,18,Fstabbed and beaten in her Lurgan home
OL,19,Fafter being subjected to what has been
OL,20,Fdescribed a "prolonged assault".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
