PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1772052053
OL,3,CYouTuber's 'live' stream shown to
OL,4,Cmurder trial jury
OL,6,FA knife found beside her body along
OL,7,Fwith an information sheet on diabetes
OL,8,Fand a silver dog bowl taken from the
OL,9,Fscene were also shown to the judge and
OL,10,Fjury today.
OL,12,FA number of agreed facts between both
OL,13,Fthe the prosecution and defence were
OL,14,Falso read out along with WhatsApp
OL,15,Fmessages including the final text from
OL,16,FNatalie to the defendant.
OL,18,FAt 17:57 on Sunday 18th December 2022,
OL,19,FMcCullagh wrote "right I'm off to
OL,20,Fstream the night away, wish me luck".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
