OL,3,CYouTuber's 'live' stream shown to
OL,4,Cmurder trial jury
OL,6,FMiss McNally replied "Good luck. I
OL,7,Fmight have a sneak peak later".
OL,9,FThe trial will continue on Thursday
OL,10,Fmorning.
